text.tspan: Cumulative number of objects launched into space
This includes satellites, probes, landers, crewed spacecrafts, and space station flight elements launched into Earth
Source: United Nations Office for Outer Space Affairs, Online Index of Objects Launched into Outer Space (2022)
Note: When an object is launched by a country on behalf of another one, it is attributed to the latter.
